{"tid":42102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"翻完學 犯賤口痕去食個公廁m記包！！！","createTime":"2016-12-16T11:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T12:12:13.000Z","uid":9722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"489b5f63cdc972564576e05409af5f2beeed2668","tid":42102,"uid":9722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"翻到屋企附近想食下d香口嘢就走咗上去間m記 見新嘢就叫黎試下啦 <br />\n落完order就喺隔離等啦 見到個出包位冼咗個包出黎 bang一聲撞完個（出包牆）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識形容呀 總之喺擋著包唔好冼出黎嘅鐵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我見到我個包反撚咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而且仲嗶咗五分一出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n熟手員工遮住好快塞翻入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係佢同廚房講差一個公廁包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個廚房好疑惑 其實喺佢出錯包 佢行出黎摞起個包 但係我留意到 佢係戴住隻藍色透明手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就喺咁戴住隻藍色透明手套改造我隻公廁包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經覺得比食屎更難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係估唔到再撲街嘅接住繼續黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個藍色透明手套廚房仔冼個公廁包出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知又撞到反肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又喺嗶五分一出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最慘嘅係執包嗰個員工自己親手拎翻入廚房 然後徒手砌翻好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我都係食咗呢個公廁包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 味道唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望今晚無咩事啦<br />\n<br />\n講翻先個公廁包喺包咗紙再加盒嘅<br />\n藍色手套喺摞生嘢用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c201a66edbabfb69f58dc80fd5fc957c491541","tid":42102,"uid":9722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"辣殺m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}